24
00:01:47,950 --> 00:01:49,789
And you should drink more water.

25
00:01:50,509 --> 00:01:54,190
Only in this way can you have a bud.

26
00:01:55,740 --> 00:01:57,370
It's a little sad,

27
00:01:57,440 --> 00:01:59,310
